summary: This is an email correspondence from July 29, 2021, regarding the service of a federal court subpoena for records, likely related to the Epstein case. The email includes an attachment of the subpoena document.

events.title: Issuance of Federal Court Subpoena
events.description: A federal court subpoena for records was issued, as indicated by the attached document filename.

events.title: Service of Subpoena via Email
events.description: An email was sent to serve the federal court subpoena for records, with the subpoena attached as a PDF.

keyFacts: A federal court subpoena for records was issued on or before July 28, 2021.
The subpoena was served via email correspondence on July 29, 2021.
The subpoena was directed to AT&T, as indicated by the attached PDF filename, suggesting a request for telecommunications records.
